trans-unit.source: This tutorial is built on GetStartedWithData, which is an Android app.
trans-unit.target: This tutorial is built on GetStartedWithData, which is an Android app.

trans-unit.source: The UI for this app is identical to the one in the Mobile Services Android quickstart, except that items that are added to the list are stored locally in memory.
trans-unit.target: The UI for this app is identical to the one in the Mobile Services Android quickstart, except that items that are added to the list are stored locally in memory.

trans-unit.source: You will add the code needed to persist the data to storage.
trans-unit.target: You will add the code needed to persist the data to storage.

trans-unit.source: Download the mobile-services-samples repository from gitHub by clicking here and then Click Download ZIP.
trans-unit.target: Download the mobile-services-samples repository from gitHub by clicking here and then Click Download ZIP.

trans-unit.source: Unzip the downloaded file and make a note of its location.
trans-unit.target: Unzip the downloaded file and make a note of its location.

trans-unit.source: In Eclipse, click File then Import, expand Android, click Existing Android Code into Workspace, and then click Next.
trans-unit.target: In Eclipse, click File then Import, expand Android, click Existing Android Code into Workspace, and then click Next.

trans-unit.source: Click Browse, browse to the location of the expanded gitHub repo that you noted earlier.
trans-unit.target: Click Browse, browse to the location of the expanded gitHub repo that you noted earlier.

trans-unit.source: Browse to the GetStartedWithData directory, and then click the Android directory.
trans-unit.target: Browse to the GetStartedWithData directory, and then click the Android directory.

trans-unit.source: Click OK, and make sure that the GetStartedWithData project is checked.
trans-unit.target: Click OK, and make sure that the GetStartedWithData project is checked.

trans-unit.source: If you want the project copied into your workspace (recommended), check the Copy projects into workspace box.
trans-unit.target: If you want the project copied into your workspace (recommended), check the Copy projects into workspace box.

trans-unit.source: This imports the project files into the current workspace.
trans-unit.target: This imports the project files into the current workspace.
